    <item>
      <title>通過 Git Submodule 安裝</title>
      <link>https://razonyang.github.io/hbs-test/zh-hant/docs/getting-started/installation/git-submodule/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Dec 2021 10:43:39 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://razonyang.github.io/hbs-test/zh-hant/docs/getting-started/installation/git-submodule/</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[This article refers to the traditional installation method of cloning the theme locally as Git submodule. While this installation method is still widely used, we recommend to install the theme as Hugo module. 從頭開始創建站點# 1$ git clone https://github.com/razonyang/hugo-theme-bootstrap-skeleton myblog 2$ cd myblog 3$ git submodule add https://github.com/razonyang/hugo-theme-bootstrap themes/hugo-theme-bootstrap 4$ sed -i &#34;s/theme:.*/theme: hugo-theme-bootstrap/g&#34; config/_default/config.yaml 5$ rm go.mod go.sum 6$ hugo mod npm]]></description>
    </item>
    
